HEADWORD: Inquirer
<hw>In*quir"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Written also
<ets>enquirer</ets>.]</ety> <def>One who inquires or examines;
questioner; investigator.</def> <rj><au>Locke.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Expert <qex>inquirers</qex> after truth.</q>
<rj><qau>Cowper.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Inquiring</ent>⟦br⟧
